DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		FILTER(
			KEEPFILTERS(
				SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
					'Consommation'[Etiquette_DPE],
					'Consommation'[adresses-69.lat.1],
					'Consommation'[adresses-69.lon.1],

					"MinEtiquette_DPE", IGNORE(CALCULATE(MIN('Consommation'[Etiquette_DPE])))
				)

			OR(
				OR(
					NOT(ISBLANK('Consommation'[Etiquette_DPE])),

				NOT(ISBLANK('Consommation'[adresses-69.lon.1]))
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount

		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(
				FILTER(
					KEEPFILTERS(
						SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
							'Consommation'[Etiquette_DPE],
							'Consommation'[adresses-69.lat.1],
							'Consommation'[adresses-69.lon.1],
							__DS0FilterTable,
							"Conso_Moyenne", IGNORE('Consommation'[Conso_Moyenne]),
							"MinEtiquette_DPE", IGNORE(CALCULATE(MIN('Consommation'[Etiquette_DPE]))),
							"CountRowsConsommation", COUNTROWS('Consommation')
						)
					),
					OR(
						OR(
							NOT(ISBLANK('Consommation'[Etiquette_DPE])),
							NOT(ISBLANK('Consommation'[adresses-69.lat.1]))
						),
						NOT(ISBLANK('Consommation'[adresses-69.lon.1]))
					)
				)
			),
			"'Consommation'[Etiquette_DPE]", 'Consommation'[Etiquette_DPE],
			"'Consommation'[adresses-69.lat.1]", 'Consommation'[adresses-69.lat.1],

			"Conso_Moyenne", [Conso_Moyenne],
			"MinEtiquette_DPE", [MinEtiquette_DPE]
		)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	ROW(
	"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
)
